    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing mechanical tactile feedback that modern dual-clutch systems lack. The chassis is sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry remains precise under lateral load. Performance is further enhanced by a factory limited-slip differential and a responsive VANOS system that has been professionally serviced. This is a driver-focused machine with a linear power band and exceptional turn-in characteristics.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
