    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor character marks expected from careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been treated with respect; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and the climate control and infotainment systems function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With a fresh set of tires and a clean title, this car is ready for its next chapter. It\u2019s a reliable, high-performing choice for a discerning driver who values quality and longevity.",
